Requirements:
===================

- Berkeley DB
    - Download the source code from http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/database/berkeleydb/downloads/index.html
    $ tar xfvz db-5.2.28.tar.gz
    $ cd db-5.2.28/build_unix
    $ ../dist/configure --prefix=/usr/local --enable-cxx
    $ make
    $ sudo make install

